{"tid":2248984,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKU][有名］如何投訴極品lecturer","createTime":"2020-10-19T04:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T10:56:47.000Z","uid":300420,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"256b5cdbd841cf8edfb1b6f56af1dbee6a0b3e90","tid":2248984,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"今日發生咗一件好仆街嘅事<br />\n話說我take咗一個叫做mgmt2401嘅course<br />\nCourse裏面有個group project<br />\n咁group project就梗係要form group<br />\n<br />\n我哋開學嗰陣時填咗份group list+group number就算 跟住之後prof+ta就冇理過我哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫email俾佢都唔撚覆 上堂講嘢又食螺絲又唔答人問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前已經出Po 屌過 不過冇開名(今日同teammate傾完之後發覺原來佢都有寫email 不過佢冇reply<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[屌你老母］奉勸各位中學雞切勿入HKU 尤其是係business related course<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2237915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2237915</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n直到今日都係冇email 不過ta尋日有正常叫我哋present<br />\n<br />\n我地present 之後佢話我地個group number錯咗<br />\n原來佢一直都有條list 係唔同我哋講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底係佢完全冇擺心機落教學工作 一直冇睇過條list 去到而家先睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係諗住專登唔講出嚟玩人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有我到而家都唔知course assessment係點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係佢嘅email: simonlam@hku.hk <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fbe.hku.hk/people/academic/simon-s-k-lam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fbe.hku.hk%2Fpeople%2Facademic%2Fsimon-s-k-lam&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=cdfd0ccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fbe.hku.hk/people/academic/simon-s-k-lam</a><br />\n<br />\n想投訴但係唔知喺邊度投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎大家幫我問吓 睇吓佢會唔會覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw Simon我知道你有mon po㗎 你都估到我係邊個啦 大家對事不對人 咪撚亂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882cbb1c8b083d03761459cb034852aaa18373f1","tid":2248984,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:35:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3332b0455f791a01ee19a37c790adf4f49857e2","tid":2248984,"uid":339100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:36:42.000Z","msg":"Hi <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195dbe7060444f11cc0c69e393e7dff2c95d8e43","tid":2248984,"uid":301116,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:44:54.000Z","msg":"密都唔加 其人勇士 宜可使<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef329f68fbe37e4948754ed1651c93f607dff72","tid":2248984,"uid":300420,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"195dbe7060444f11cc0c69e393e7dff2c95d8e43","tid":2248984,"uid":301116,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:44:54.000Z","msg":"密都唔加 其人勇士 宜可使<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:47:34.000Z","msg":"梗係而家投訴發大佢啦<br />\nSem尾冇仇報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢搞得嚟隨時又有另一班人賴嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/